name: Liberty Electric Cars
overview:
Liberty Electric Cars designs, develops and produces leading edge electric vehicle technologies and vehicles to serve growing demand for zero-emission transport solutions in markets around the world.

It then goes on to take care of these vehicles once sold through a team of highly trained and experienced EV professionals.

Our experienced and highly skilled engineers have invented, IP-protected innovative electric vehicle (EV) drive train technologies that can be employed in a wide variety of vehicle platforms like trucks, buses, 4x4, SUV, MPV, pick up trucks. Liberty Electric Cars has recently reinforced its engineering team and now has one of the most experienced teams in EV technology in the world. This unique team of engineers have created EVs that have driven over 2,500,000 miles - the greatest distance and thus best experience of any electric vehicle team in the world.
